text: Kye Francis Rowles (born 24 June 1998) is an Australian soccer player. He plays for D.C. United in the MLS and for the Australia men's national soccer team (nicknamed the "Socceroos"). ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Australian men's soccer players Category:Sportspeople from New South Wales Category:2022 FIFA World Cup players
